name: Michele Laub
who_you_serve: Professionals and individuals seeking coaching, consulting, and personal development services.

jv_history.source_quote: Dr. Laub became a psychiatrist and psychoanalyst and settled in New Haven where he was affiliated with the Yale Medical School. Together with Laurel Vlock

what_you_do: When Michele Laub was first introduced to the game-changing work of don Miguel Ruiz about The Four Agreements, she was called to get certified as a facilitator in his simple, yet life-changing agreements to create a more gratifying life.
social_proof: She is one of the few facilitators around the world certified in this life-enhancing approach.
niche: life coaching, self-improvement, mental health, spirituality, relationships
business_focus: Guiding people to embrace the principles of The Four Agreements to create a more gratifying life.
